### PHICS Integration Configuration
```bash
# PHICS (Phoenix Hot-Reloading Integration Container System)
PHICS_ENABLED=true
CONTAINER_ENFORCEMENT=true  
WORKSPACE_MOUNT=/workspace:z
HOT_RELOAD_MODE=bidirectional
FILE_SYNC=active
```

